version_description:
- Hide "My Interests" side of the planner if reserved seating is unavailable.
- Default to show past Agenda items.
- Agenda filters will only appear if there are several options per filter category.

Minor release to:
- Maintain caching of the last event visited, consistently for both platforms
- Allow users to use the app after a day, without having to re-enter login credentials

- Minor bug fixes
- Enabled translations
- Upgraded Dependencies
